She's not going to win anything.

57
00:04:22,088 --> 00:04:25,064
Well, thank you for
 that vote of confidence.

58
00:04:25,064 --> 00:04:29,353
That's it.  I'm playing Juliet, 
and nothing is going to stop me.

59
00:04:29,353 --> 00:04:33,628
