It seems she hangs upon 
the cheek of night. / Niles...Niles...

72
00:05:24,745 --> 00:05:27,157
Yes?  What?
 / Don't I come in here somewhere?

73
00:05:27,157 --> 00:05:29,994
And on and on.  Beauty to rich
 for youth but a...

